KCAPTCHA plug-in for MediaWiki ConfirmEdit extension

LICENSE: GNU GPLv3

USAGE:
1) Download ConfirmEdit extension into extensions/ConfirmEdit
2) Download this extension into extensions/WikiKCaptcha
3) Put the following lines into your LocalSettings.php:

   require_once "$IP/extensions/ConfirmEdit/ConfirmEdit.php";
   require_once "$IP/extensions/ConfirmEdit/WikiKCaptcha.class.php";
   $wgCaptchaClass = 'WikiKCaptcha';
4) Optionally configure CAPTCHA triggers
   See http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:ConfirmEdit#Configuration
